Configure Census Management for Group Benefits Quoting
The Quote Census Lightning web component shows group members, dependents, and plan selections. Validation rules flag exceptions and users can add and edit data all in one place. The hierarchical tree view helps browse through large, detailed data sets.
The Quote Census Lightning web component gives users a straightforward way to incorporate census data into a quote. After configuring the component and incorporating it into workflows, insurance carrier administrators and brokers upload census data, identify and correct data exceptions, and turn quotes into contracts.
Customize the Quote Census Lightning web component for user workflows and create rules that ensure users get cleanest census data possible.
